Check Stan

check_cmdstanr.Rd

Check whether cmdstanr is available and prints version and logistic example.

Usage

check_cmdstanr()

Examples

check_cmdstanr()
#> cmdstan version: 
#> [1] "2.31.0"

#> data {
#>   int<lower=0> N;
